#################################################
THM-Cards

to install all needed node modules:
install nodejs and npm on your HOST machine
on your HOST Machine:
go into the thmcards directory
run: npm install --loglevel info --no-bin-links

(npm can cause problems when run from a vagrant machine,
running from your host will be safer)


to setup the couchDB:
./init.sh

to start THM-Cards:
./start.sh

press ctrl+c to end THM-Cards

#################################################
